snippet.title: Married at First Sight: Amber and Dave's Religious Views Don't Align (S7, E5) | Lifetime
snippet.description:
Dave realizes that he may not have been clear enough with the experts about his own faith or what he expects of Amber in this clip from Season 7, Episode 5, "Trouble in Paradise."#MarriedAtFirstSight
